        </div>
        <div>
            <h4 id="toast-title" class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-1">Appointment Request Sent</h4>
            <p id="toast-body" class="text-sm opacity-80 leading-relaxed">We will call you at 246-253-3387 to finalize your booking.</p>
